---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Support — Fractune">
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo"><img src="/logo.png" alt="" class="nav-logo-icon" />Fractune</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="page">
    <div class="page-inner">
      <h1>Support</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">We're happy to help. Here are the most common questions.</p>

      <h2>What is a D-value?</h2>
      <p>
        The D-value is the fractal dimension calculated using the box-counting
        method. A value close to 1.0 indicates simple geometry (e.g. a smooth
        concrete wall), while values closer to 2.0 indicate high complexity
        (e.g. ornamented facades).
      </p>

      <h2>How do I analyse a building?</h2>
      <p>
        Open Fractune, point the camera at a building facade, and tap the
        analyse button. Make sure the facade is evenly lit and fills most of
        the screen for best results.
      </p>

      <h2>Can I delete my data?</h2>
      <p>
        Yes. Send an email to <a href="mailto:privacy@fractune.dk">privacy@fractune.dk</a>
        with your contributor ID (found under Settings in the app). We will
        delete all your contributions within 30 days.
      </p>

      <h2>The app isn't working — what do I do?</h2>
      <p>
        Try restarting the app and make sure you have the latest version from
        the App Store. If the problem persists, contact us at
        <a href="mailto:support@fractune.dk">support@fractune.dk</a> with a
        description and your iOS version.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="mailto:support@fractune.dk">support@fractune.dk</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .nav { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .nav-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    height: 52px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .nav-logo { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.375rem; }
  .nav-logo-icon { height: 1.0em; width: auto; vertical-align: middle; transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .page { padding: 4rem 0; }
  .page-inner { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
  h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .subtitle { color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 1.0625rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  p { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
</style>
